  "detailed_description": "Click Painter is a puzzle game where you solve puzzles logically and draw colorful pictures in a comfortable atmosphere. Become a painter and draw a picture to be displayed at Armi's museum in crisis!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/f4fe16825fd61d3fdeb05d25a9351728.poster.avif?t=1762853114\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/f4fe16825fd61d3fdeb05d25a9351728.webm?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/f4fe16825fd61d3fdeb05d25a9351728.mp4?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/cf878db98e3f7cf62ed6e9b5ae3cbefd.poster.avif?t=1762853114\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/cf878db98e3f7cf62ed6e9b5ae3cbefd.webm?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>In Click Painter, you solve puzzles and complete paintings using the advanced Minesweeper rules without any guessing. Each cell is presented with one or more numbers, telling you how much paint of the same color as the number should be around it. Based on the numbers provided, infer which paint should be painted in which cell, and paint the correct paint in the correct location!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/3ade910f241295cd70f4b28b468fb86a.poster.avif?t=1762853114\" width=600 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/3ade910f241295cd70f4b28b468fb86a.webm?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/3ade910f241295cd70f4b28b468fb86a.mp4?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you solve the puzzle at your own pace in a comfortable and soothing atmosphere, you will soon have finished a colorful picture. Puppy, dragon, harmonica, snowman, wizard, etc.. Draw a variety of pictures!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/39862c3502f44c92f864c7cf11b27316.avif?t=1762853114\" width=592 height=300 /></span><br><br>The more pictures you complete, the more achievements and fun animations you can get.<br>Collect all achievements and animations!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/0c4aa0acc0ba75918677959e6f9cc3c9.avif?t=1762853114\" width=300 height=300 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/70676f621cbb7a4bef95a887dba7f0e1.gif?t=1762853114\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/70676f621cbb7a4bef95a887dba7f0e1.poster.avif?t=1762853114\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Novel and challenging puzzles<br></li><li>Relaxing and soothing atmosphere<br></li><li>About 100 colorful stages<br></li><li>All puzzles are solvable<br></li><li>Various achievements and special animations<br></li><li>Additional random and custom modes to enjoy</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Click Painter is a puzzle game where you solve puzzles logically and draw colorful pictures in a comfortable atmosphere. Become a painter and draw a picture to be displayed at Armi's museum in crisis!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/f4fe16825fd61d3fdeb05d25a9351728.poster.avif?t=1762853114\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/f4fe16825fd61d3fdeb05d25a9351728.webm?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/f4fe16825fd61d3fdeb05d25a9351728.mp4?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/cf878db98e3f7cf62ed6e9b5ae3cbefd.poster.avif?t=1762853114\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/cf878db98e3f7cf62ed6e9b5ae3cbefd.webm?t=1762853114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>In Click Painter, you solve puzzles and complete paintings using the advanced Minesweeper rules without any guessing. Each cell is presented with one or more numbers, telling you how much paint of the same color as the number should be around it. Based on the numbers provided, infer which paint should be painted in which cell, and paint the correct paint in the correct location!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063040/extras/3ade910f241295cd70f4b28b468fb86a.poster.avif?t=1762853114\" width=600 height=380 ><source src=\"https: